data.description: Beautiful acreage inside the city limits!  Property is currently being used for agriculture but is zoned by the city as Industrial 1 and Industrial 2.  So Many Possibilities with this!  Could be developed into large acre+ estate lots to create a beautiful subdivision.  You could build your dream home and farm the land or just have a beautiful rolling estate!  Includes a pond surrounded by beautiful trees!  Utilities & Fiber optic cable would be accessible from the main road but are not currently on the property.  Located within the Gallatin school district and conveniently within approximately 1 mile of elementary & high school as well as downtown.  All taxes, measurements, schools & numbers to be verified by buyer and/or buyer's agent.  Survey recommended for accurate boundaries.
